ly pay when we successfully collect the debt for you, aligning our interests with yours. By utilizing our services, you not only minimize your financial risk but also leverage our industry expertise in dealing with cannabis-related debts. We understand the complexities and regulations of the cannabis industry, which enables us to tailor our collection strategies to maximize your recovery. Choose Legal Collects, and let us help you recover what&#8217;s rightfully yours without the burden of additional upfront costs.</div>\n			</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_2_5 et_pb_column_8  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_image et_pb_image_0\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<span class=\"et_pb_image_wrap \"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"750\" height=\"750\" src=\"http://legalcollects.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legal-collect-1.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"legal-collect (1)\" srcset=\"http://legalcollects.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legal-collect-1.png 750w, http://legalcollects.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legal-collect-1-480x480.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 750px, 100vw\" class=\"wp-image-433\" /></span>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_5 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_9  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_7  et_pb_text_align_center et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">Debt collections, specifically for the cannabis industry</div>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_6 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters2\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_10  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_2 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">Leading  cannabis collection agency in the US</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_8  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">As the dominant brand name for cannabis debt collections, debtors in the marijuana business are more likely to respond and pay when they hear from Legal Collects.</div>\n			</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_11  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_3 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">Cannabis client and debtor database in the industry</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_9  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">We utilize our database of 1000+ clients and 7500+ debtor claims. The most debtor data compared to any other agency. Information and connections mean power.</div>\n			</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3 et_pb_column_12  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_4 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">Over $130M of cannabis processed debt</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_10  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">Our specialized expertise ensures efficient and effective recovery within the unique regulatory landscape of the cannabis industry. You don’t pay us if we can’t collect.</div>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_7\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_13  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_1_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_center et_pb_button_alignment_tablet_center et_pb_button_alignment_phone_center et_pb_module \">\n				<a class=\"et_pb_button et_pb_button_1 et_pb_bg_layout_light\" href=\"http://legalcollects.local/about-us/\">Learn More About Us</a>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_8 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_3_5 et_pb_column_14  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_5 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">Cannabis debt collection agency or cannabis law firm?</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_11  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">While a cannabis law firm is undoubtedly essential for various legal matters within the cannabis industry, when it comes to collecting past-due accounts or taking legal action to recover unpaid invoices, choosing a specialized cannabis debt collection agency like Legal Collects offers a distinct advantage. We operate on a contingency fee basis, meaning you only pay us if we successfully collect the debt. This approach significantly reduces the financial burden on your business, as opposed to the traditional hourly billing structure of cannabis law firms. If legal action becomes necessary to collect your money, our expert team of attorneys across the nation can step in, st