(2479,	455,	'_et_pb_truncate_post',	'<div class=\"et_pb_section et_pb_section_3 et_pb_with_background et_section_regular\" >\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_13 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_24  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_7 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">How can a cannabis collection agency help your business?</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_14  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">At Legal Collects, we pride ourselves on being the first and leading cannabis debt collection agency, dedicated to helping businesses in the cannabis industry recover outstanding debts while navigating the unique legal and regulatory challenges of this rapidly evolving field. Our Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) section is a valuable resource for clients and potential partners, providing insight into our comprehensive debt recovery solutions and compliance expertise. Whether you&#8217;re curious about the debt collection process specific to the cannabis industry or seeking answers to common queries about our agency&#8217;s capabilities, our FAQs section is designed to offer clarity and transparency. </div>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_14 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_25  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_8 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">DEBT COLLECTION</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_with_border et_pb_module difl_faq difl_faq_0\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_wrapper \" data-settings=\'{\"faq_layout\":\"accordion\",\"activate_on_first_time\":\"off\",\"active_item_order_number\":0,\"faq_animation\":\"slide\",\"faq_anime_duration\":\"300\",\"icon_animation\":\"fade\",\"que_img_animation\":\"fade\",\"content_animation_type\":\"fade_in\",\"content_anime_duration\":\"250\",\"order_class\":\"difl_faq_0\",\"faq_layout_grid\":\"off\",\"faq_item_per_column\":\"2\",\"faq_item_per_column_tablet\":\"2\",\"faq_item_per_column_phone\":\"1\"}\'><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_0\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Why choose a cannabis collection agency over a law firm or attorney?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>A cannabis specialized collection agency is the top choice over retaining an hourly law firm or attorney. Since Legal Collects is purely a contingent agency you bear zero risk if your debtor either decides not to pay or does not have the funds to pay. Attorneys will bill you regardless of a successful outcome which can result in high legal fees without a successful result. Moreso, many business attorneys and law firms do not specialze in collections and are not the optimal bill collectors. Legal Collects is comprised with a commercial collection law background, but with the power, persistency and dominance as the leading collection agency in the cannabis and cbd industry.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_1\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Who is the best debt collection agency for cannabis companies?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects is the best debt collection agency for cannabis companies. Founded with more than 35 years of collection industry experience and along side former cannabis operators. Legal Collects is uniquely equipped to handle every cannabis related accounts receivable issue throughout USA and Canada, both adult-use and medical. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_2\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Why choose Legal Collects to collect on behalf of your cannabis business?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects is uniquely positioned to be the leader in cannnabis and cbd related collection matters for 2 reasons. #1: Legal Collects is the first and leading collection agency focused solely within the cannabis industry. This creates a major advantage in regards to our understanding, database and connections in the industry to yield a quicker and higher success rate than other agencies. #2: All claims received by Legal Collects is managed by Ross Gelfand, who has over years of commercial collection and collection law experience. Ross previously represented fortune 500 accounts such as Capital One and Honda, managing over 150 collectors and a full legal team. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_3\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Why choose Legal Collects for cannabis accounts receivable services?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects understands how to successfully manage first party receivables while also understanding the importance of reputation and superb customer service in the cannabis industry. Legal Collects offers multiple options including hourly or contingency to handle first party receivables prior to the accounts needing to be sent to collections. With our large database of cannabis clients and database, we can utilize our own resources and network to ensure we do everything possible to get your accounts to pay prior to needing collection efforts.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_4\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">What is Legal Collect\'s success rate?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects typically is yielding around a 80%+ success rate depending on the quality of the claim. Since we have worked thousands of cannabis related claims, we know quickly if we are willing to take on a specific claim or not. This not only helps save us time and effort but also our client to make the best next decision as soon as possible. Our database and experience helps to ensure the highest success rate in the industry for cannabis related collections. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_5\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Benefits of a Commercial Cannabis Debt Collection Agency</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects is the first and leading collection agency focused solely within the cannabis industry. This creates a major advantage in regards to our understanding, database and connections in the industry to yield a quicker and higher success rate than other agencies. Our agency understands how to speak the lingo specific to the cannabis industry while also being well connected to the good and bad actors in the space. More so we are able to provide our clients with various referrals and networking opportunities based on their needs since Legal Collects is heavily tied into the cannabis industry.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_6\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Who are examples of Legal Collects clients?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects represent a wide range of different clients that are doing business in the cannabis and cbd industry. These range from any of the growers, producers, or distributors selling directly to dispensaries and retailers. Our firm also represents many ancillary cannabis companies including marketing agencies, staffing, grow supply, lighting, law firms, etc that are owed money from various cannabis and cbd clients. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_7\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">What happens if Legal Collects can’t collect?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>If Legal Collects can&#8217;t collect there is zero risk to our client. Since we are solely a contingency only agency, if we cannot collect, our clients don&#8217;t pay. Period. In other words we take on all the risk to collect on an account and if we are unsuccessful the client can decide to take back the claim to write it off or has the option to escalate the matter to legal. We work with associated attorneys from across the country to litigate claims on behalf of our clients if we are unsuccessful with our collection efforts. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div></div>\r\n            \n				</div>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_15 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_26  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_4_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_right et_pb_module \">\n				<a class=\"et_pb_button et_pb_button_4 et_pb_bg_layout_light\" href=\"http://legalcollects.local/debt-collections/\">Learn More</a>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_16 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_27  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_heading et_pb_heading_9 et_pb_bg_layout_\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_heading_container\"><h2 class=\"et_pb_module_heading\">LEGAL NETWORK</h2></div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_with_border et_pb_module difl_faq difl_faq_1\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_wrapper \" data-settings=\'{\"faq_layout\":\"accordion\",\"activate_on_first_time\":\"off\",\"active_item_order_number\":0,\"faq_animation\":\"slide\",\"faq_anime_duration\":\"300\",\"icon_animation\":\"fade\",\"que_img_animation\":\"fade\",\"content_animation_type\":\"fade_in\",\"content_anime_duration\":\"250\",\"order_class\":\"difl_faq_1\",\"faq_layout_grid\":\"off\",\"faq_item_per_column\":\"2\",\"faq_item_per_column_tablet\":\"2\",\"faq_item_per_column_phone\":\"1\"}\'><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_8\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">What is \'Legal Collects\' legal network, and how does it work?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Legal Collects has a specialized nation-wide legal network that consists of experienced attorneys and legal experts with in-depth knowledge of the cannabis industry. If our collectors are unable to recover your unpaid invoice, we can recommend escalating the claim to legal action.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_9\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">When should I consider involving \'Legal Collects\' legal network for my unpaid invoice?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>If our collection efforts are unsuccessful and the debtor remains uncooperative, it may be advisable to involve our legal network. They can assess the situation and provide guidance on the best course of action.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_10\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">How does the contingency fee arrangement with your legal network work?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Our legal network works on a contingency fee basis, which means they only charge a fee if they successfully recover the debt. This fee is a percentage of the amount collected. Please contact us to learn more about our rates and processes. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_11\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Is involving your legal network the final step in the debt collection process?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>While legal action is an option, it is not the final step. Our goal is always to recover the debt as efficiently as possible. Legal action is pursued when other collection methods have been exhausted.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_12\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Can I choose my own attorney, or do I have to use \'Legal Collects\' legal network?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>While you have the option to choose your attorney, working with our legal network ensures that you have access to professionals with expertise in cannabis debt recovery, which can be a significant advantage. By using our services, you will not have to pay an hourly fee and will only pay a contingency fee on the amount that is collected. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_13\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">What is the success rate of recovering unpaid invoices through legal action with \'Legal Collects\' legal network?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>The success rate can vary depending on the circumstances of each case. Our legal experts will assess the viability of legal action and provide you with an honest assessment of the chances of recovery.</div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_module difl_faqitem difl_faqitem_14\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_module_inner\">\n					<div class=\"df_faq_item\" data-settings=\'{\"hide_faq_item\":\"\"}\'>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_question_area\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"faq_question\"><h2 class=\"faq_question_title\">Do I need to provide any specific documentation or evidence to involve Legal Collects\' legal network in my case?</h2></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"faq_icon\"><div class=\"close_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4c;</span></div>\r\n                <div class=\"open_icon\"><span class=\"et-pb-icon\">&#x4b;</span></div></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          \r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"faq_answer_area\">\r\n                   <div class=\"faq_content\">\r\n                        <div class=\"faq_answer\"><div>Yes, providing all relevant documentation, including the unpaid invoice, communication records, and any relevant contracts, can help our legal network assess the strength of your case and proceed more effectively. These documents will first be used by our team of debt collectors and then sent to our legal network when suing. </div> </div>\r\n                        \r\n                   </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\n				</div>\n			</div></div>\r\n            \n				</div>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div><div class=\"et_pb_row et_pb_row_17 et_pb_equal_columns et_pb_gutters3\">\n				<div class=\"et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_28  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\">\n				\n				\n				\n				\n				<div class=\"et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_5_wrapper et_pb_button_alignment_right et_pb_module \">\n				<a class=\"et_pb_button et_pb_button_5 et_pb_bg_layout_light\" href=\"http://legalcollects.local/legal-network/\">Learn More</a>\n			</div>\n			</div>\n				\n				\n				\n				\n			</div>\n				\n				\n			</div>\n'),
