_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" toggle_line_height_tablet=\"22px\" toggle_line_height_phone=\"22px\" toggle_line_height_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" body_font_size_tablet=\"15px\" body_font_size_phone=\"15px\" body_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" body_line_height_tablet=\"21px\" body_line_height_phone=\"21px\" body_line_height_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" border_width_all=\"0px\" border_width_top=\"1px\" border_color_top=\"#afafaf\" border_width_bottom=\"1px\" border_color_bottom=\"#afafaf\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"Where can Legal Collects escalate to legal action in the US to collect past-due invoices?\" open=\"on\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_top=\"none\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\"]<p>Legal Collects boasts the capability to escalate to legal proceedings in every legal cannabis state across the United States. Our extensive network of cannabis lawyers ensures that we can effectively proceed with litigation to recover your outstanding debts, regardless of the state where the cannabis debtor company resides.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"How does CannaBIZ Collects ensure effective legal representation in cannabis-related debt collection cases?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>We have strategically developed a network of experienced cannabis lawyers who specialize in debt collection within the cannabis industry. Each lawyer in our network possesses a deep understanding of the unique legal nuances surrounding cannabis laws in their respective states. This expertise allows us to provide tailored legal representation to effectively pursue debt collection on your behalf.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What costs are involved when escalating to legal action with Legal Collects?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>When you approve legal action on your file and our team recommends escalation, you will only be responsible for covering the pass-through court costs required to file the lawsuit. Following this, our fee structure operates on a contingency basis. You will only pay a flat contingency fee out of the funds successfully collected by our associate legal counsel. This means no upfront hourly rates – it\'s a \"No collection. No Fee. Period.\" policy.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What happens if standard cannabis debt collection methods are ineffective?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>If our debt collection efforts fail, we transition to our legal phase, utilizing our expertise in the cannabis industry and our extensive nation-wide legal network to escalate and sue the debtor.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What is Legal Collect\'s success rate?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p><span>Legal Collects typically is yielding around a 80%+ success rate depending on the quality of the claim. Since we have worked thousands of cannabis related claims, we know quickly if we are willing to take on a specific claim or not. This not only helps save us time and effort but also our client to make the best next decision as soon as possible. Our database and experience helps to ensure the highest success rate in the industry for cannabis related collections. </span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"Benefits of a Commercial Cannabis Debt Collection Agency\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p><span>Legal Collects is the first and leading collection agency focused solely within the cannabis industry. This creates a major advantage in regards to our understanding, database and connections in the industry to yield a quicker and higher success rate than other agencies. Our agency understands how to speak the lingo specific to the cannabis industry while also being well connected to the good and bad actors in the space. More so we are able to provide our clients with various referrals and networking opportunities based on their needs since Legal Collects is heavily tied into the cannabis industry.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"Who are examples of Legal Collects clients?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p><span>Legal Collects represent a wide range of different clients that are doing business in the cannabis and cbd industry. These range from any of the growers, producers, or distributors selling directly to dispensaries and retailers. Our firm also represents many ancillary cannabis companies including marketing agencies, staffing, grow supply, lighting, law firms, etc that are owed money from various cannabis and cbd clients. </span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What happens if Legal Collects can’t collect my money?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p><span>If Legal Collects can\'t collect there is zero risk to our client. Since we are solely a contingency only agency, if we cannot collect, our clients don\'t pay. Period. In other words we take on all the risk to collect on an account and if we are unsuccessful the client can decide to take back the claim to write it off or has the option to escalate the matter to legal. We work with associated attorneys from across the country to litigate claims on behalf of our clients if we are unsuccessful with our collection efforts. </span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What are the steps involved in debt collection with Legal Collects?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p class=\"\">Initially, our expert debt collectors strategize to recover debts. If needed, we seamlessly escalate to legal action, all while keeping clients informed and involved.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"How does Legal Collects ensure cost-effective debt recovery when suing and using cannabis attorneys?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>By operating on a contingency fee basis, clients only pay if we successfully collect the money owed to them, eliminating the burden of costly hourly legal fees.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"What sets Legal Collects apart from other debt collection agencies?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>Our holistic approach, combining expert debt collectors with a state-by-state legal network, ensures effective debt recovery tailored to the cannabis industry\'s complexities.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"How does Legal Collects support businesses in the cannabis market?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>We stand as a beacon of support for businesses navigating the complexities of debt collection, offering tailored solutions and expert guidance in the ever-evolving landscape of the cannabis industry.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=\"Is legal action the final step in the debt collection process with Legal Collects?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"||0px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||false|false\" custom_padding_phone=\"|||0px|false|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" border_style_bottom=\"none\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" open=\"off\"]<p>While legal action may be necessary in some cases, it is not always the final step in our debt collection process. Our approach is holistic, aiming to resolve debt collection challenges efficiently and effectively. Following legal escalation, if required, we continue to pursue all available avenues for debt recovery, ensuring the best possible outcome for our clients.</p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][/et_pb_accordion][et_pb_button button_url=\"http://legalcollects.local/contact-us/\" button_text=\"Contact us\" button_alignment=\"center\" button_alignment_tablet=\"center\" button_alignment_phone=\"center\" button_alignment_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"18px\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#1f8e1f\" button_border_width=\"0px\" button_border_color=\"#1f8e1f\" button_border_radius=\"30px\" button_font=\"proxima-bold|700|||||||\" button_use_icon=\"off\" custom_margin=\"||||false|false\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||20px||false|false\" custom_margin_phone=\"||20px||false|false\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_padding=\"10px|30px|10px|30px|true|true\" custom_padding_tablet=\"10px|30px|10px|30px|true|true\" custom_padding_phone=\"10px|30px|10px|30px|true|true\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" hover_transition_duration=\"1000ms\" hover_transition_delay=\"-150ms\" button_text_size_tabl