eight=\"26px\" text_font_size_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" text_font_size_tablet=\"18px\" text_line_height_tablet=\"25px\" text_font_size_phone=\"16px\" text_line_height_phone=\"23px\"]<p><span>At Legal Collects, we pride ourselves on being the first and leading cannabis debt collection agency, dedicated to helping businesses in the cannabis industry recover outstanding debts while navigating the unique legal and regulatory challenges of this rapidly evolving field. Our Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) section is a valuable resource for clients and potential partners, providing insight into our comprehensive debt recovery solutions and compliance expertise. Whether you\'re curious about the debt collection process specific to the cannabis industry or seeking answers to common queries about our agency\'s capabilities, our FAQs section is designed to offer clarity and transparency. </span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" make_equal=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" width=\"90%\" max_width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" max_width=\"1400px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" width_tablet=\"90%\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" custom_padding_tablet=\"0px||0px||false|false\" width_phone=\"90%\" max_width_tablet=\"1400px\" max_width_phone=\"1400px\" custom_padding_phone=\"0px||0px||false|false\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_heading title=\"DEBT COLLECTION\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" title_level=\"h2\" title_font=\"Proxima Nova Bold-1|700|||||||\" title_text_color=\"#333333\" title_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" title_font_size=\"40px\" title_line_height=\"45px\" title_line_height_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" title_font_size_tablet=\"30px\" title_line_height_tablet=\"40px\" title_font_size_phone=\"28px\" title_line_height_phone=\"35px\"][/et_pb_heading][difl_faq faq_item_per_column_tablet=\"2\" faq_item_per_column_phone=\"1\" faq_item_per_column_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" border_style_all_que_wrapper_border=\"none\" border_style_all_faq_item_wrapper_border=\"none\" border_style_top_faq_item_wrapper_border=\"solid\" border_style_bottom_faq_item_wrapper_border=\"solid\" border_width_bottom_faq_item_wrapper_border=\"0px\" que_wrapper_padding=\"5px|5px|0px|5px|false|false\" faq_item_gap=\"14px\" question_text_font=\"Proxima Nova Bold-1||||||||\" question_text_text_color=\"#38bd8f\" border_color_all_faq_item_wrapper_border=\"#8c8c8c\" question_text_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" question_text_font_size=\"20px\" question_text_line_height_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" question_text_line_height=\"25px\" design_answer_text_font=\"proximanova regular||||||||\" design_answer_text_text_color=\"#333333\" design_answer_text_font_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" design_answer_text_font_size=\"16px\" design_answer_text_line_height_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" design_answer_text_line_height=\"22px\" question_text_font_size_tablet=\"18px\" question_text_line_height_tablet=\"24px\" faq_item_wrapper_bg_bgcolor=\"#f5f5f5\" question_text_font_size_phone=\"18px\" question_text_line_height_phone=\"24px\" design_answer_text_font_size_tablet=\"16px\" design_answer_text_font_size_phone=\"16px\" design_answer_text_line_height_tablet=\"22px\" design_answer_text_line_height_phone=\"22px\"][difl_faqitem question=\"Why choose a cannabis collection agency over a law firm or attorney?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover=\"1px||||false|false\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>A cannabis specialized collection agency is the top choice over retaining an hourly law firm or attorney. Since Legal Collects is purely a contingent agency you bear zero risk if your debtor either decides not to pay or does not have the funds to pay. Attorneys will bill you regardless of a successful outcome which can result in high legal fees without a successful result. Moreso, many business attorneys and law firms do not specialze in collections and are not the optimal bill collectors. Legal Collects is comprised with a commercial collection law background, but with the power, persistency and dominance as the leading collection agency in the cannabis and cbd industry.</span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"Who is the best debt collection agency for cannabis companies?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover=\"1px||||false|false\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects is the best debt collection agency for cannabis companies. Founded with more than 35 years of collection industry experience and along side former cannabis operators. Legal Collects is uniquely equipped to handle every cannabis related accounts receivable issue throughout USA and Canada, both adult-use and medical. </span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"Why choose Legal Collects to collect on behalf of your cannabis business?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" hover_enabled=\"0\" global_colors_info=\"{}\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover=\"1px||||false|false\" que_wrapper_bg_bgcolor__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects is uniquely positioned to be the leader in cannnabis and cbd related collection matters for 2 reasons. #1: Legal Collects is the first and leading collection agency focused solely within the cannabis industry. This creates a major advantage in regards to our understanding, database and connections in the industry to yield a quicker and higher success rate than other agencies. #2: All claims received by Legal Collects is managed by Ross Gelfand, who has over years of commercial collection and collection law experience. Ross previously represented fortune 500 accounts such as Capital One and Honda, managing over 150 collectors and a full legal team. </span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"Why choose Legal Collects for cannabis accounts receivable services?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects understands how to successfully manage first party receivables while also understanding the importance of reputation and superb customer service in the cannabis industry. Legal Collects offers multiple options including hourly or contingency to handle first party receivables prior to the accounts needing to be sent to collections. With our large database of cannabis clients and database, we can utilize our own resources and network to ensure we do everything possible to get your accounts to pay prior to needing collection efforts.</span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"What is Legal Collect\'s success rate?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects typically is yielding around a 80%+ success rate depending on the quality of the claim. Since we have worked thousands of cannabis related claims, we know quickly if we are willing to take on a specific claim or not. This not only helps save us time and effort but also our client to make the best next decision as soon as possible. Our database and experience helps to ensure the highest success rate in the industry for cannabis related collections. </span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"Benefits of a Commercial Cannabis Debt Collection Agency\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects is the first and leading collection agency focused solely within the cannabis industry. This creates a major advantage in regards to our understanding, database and connections in the industry to yield a quicker and higher success rate than other agencies. Our agency understands how to speak the lingo specific to the cannabis industry while also being well connected to the good and bad actors in the space. More so we are able to provide our clients with various referrals and networking opportunities based on their needs since Legal Collects is heavily tied into the cannabis industry.</span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"Who are examples of Legal Collects clients?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>Legal Collects represent a wide range of different clients that are doing business in the cannabis and cbd industry. These range from any of the growers, producers, or distributors selling directly to dispensaries and retailers. Our firm also represents many ancillary cannabis companies including marketing agencies, staffing, grow supply, lighting, law firms, etc that are owed money from various cannabis and cbd clients. </span></p>[/difl_faqitem][difl_faqitem question=\"What happens if Legal Collects can’t collect?\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" question_title_tag=\"h2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\"]<p><span>If Legal Collects can\'t collect there is zero risk to our client. Since we are solely a contingency only agency, if we cannot collect, our clients don\'t pay. Period. In other words we take on all the risk to collect on an account and if we are unsuccessful the client can decide to take back the claim to write it off or has the option to escalate the matter to legal. We work with associated attorneys from across the country to litigate claims on behalf of our clients if we are unsuccessful with our collection efforts. </span></p>[/difl_faqitem][/difl_faq][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" make_equal=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" width=\"90%\" max_width_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" max_width=\"1400px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" custom_padding=\"||||true|false\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_padding_phone=\"0px||||false|false\" width_tablet=\"90%\" width_phone=\"90%\" max_width_tablet=\"1400px\" max_width_phone=\"1400px\" custom_padding_tablet=\"||||true|false\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\"][et_pb_button button_text=\"Learn More\" _builder_version=\"4.27.4\" _module_preset=\"default\" theme_builder_area=\"post_content\" button_alignment=\"right\" sticky_enabled=\"0\" button_alignment_tablet=\"center\" button_alignment_phone=\"center\" button_alignment_last_edited=\"off|desktop\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"18px\" button_text_size_tablet=\"17px\" button_text_size_phone=\"15px\" button_text_size_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_text_color__hover=\"#1f8e1f\" button_text_color__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" button_text_color_tablet=\"#FFFFFF\" button_text_color_phone=\"#FFFFFF\" button_text_color_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" button_bg_color=\"#1f8e1f\" button_bg_color__hover=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color__hover_enabled=\"on|hover\" button_border_width=\